Please follow the below steps to run the app


1. run the FE using visual studio code (FE was written with reactJS) 

GUI was created to make your life very easy (look at the other readme file for endpoint and stracture details)

2. run the backEnd with your IDE please note that it is a spring project with lombok 

3. when both services are running try to go to 

http://localhost:7074/customer/hello 

if you see hello port 7074 it means BE is live 

4. go to http://localhost:7074/customer/init 

5. go to port localhost:3000 or any other opened by your server (npm start ) 

6. enjoy your usage of the app you should be able to handle it very easy incase of questions you may contact me  
